Get U SPORTS football kicking stats

Source: R/football_kicking.R
football_kicking.Rd

Get U SPORTS football kicking stats

Usage

football_kicking(year = c())

Arguments

year

The season(s) of interest.

Value

A tibble.

Examples

football_kicking(2018)
